          <h2>Signs Your Ducts Need Cleaning</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Visible dust around vents:</strong> Dust buildup on registers indicates dirty ducts</li>
            <li><strong>Musty or stale odors:</strong> Often indicates mold growth in ductwork</li>
            <li><strong>Allergy symptoms at home:</strong> Dirty ducts circulate allergens throughout your home</li>
            <li><strong>Excessive dust on surfaces:</strong> If you're dusting constantly, dirty ducts may be the source</li>
            <li><strong>Visible mold:</strong> Any visible mold around vents or in ducts requires immediate attention</li>
            <li><strong>Recent construction or renovation:</strong> Construction dust settles in ductwork</li>
            <li><strong>New home purchase:</strong> You don't know when ducts were last cleaned</li>
            <li><strong>Pest evidence:</strong> Signs of rodents or insects in your ductwork</li>
          </ul>

