            <li>There is visible mold growth inside ducts or on other HVAC components</li>
            <li>Ducts are infested with vermin (rodents or insects)</li>
            <li>Ducts are clogged with excessive dust and debris</li>
          </ul>
          <p>Additionally, consider duct cleaning if:</p>
